=== Value Forms

Use_Value is the usefulness of a product the end user {consumer}.  This is measures 

Exchange_Value is the difference between Consumer_Price and Owner_costs {any type of economic_rent, interest_bearing debt, profit}.  This measures Source missalocation, and is 0 when consumers owns for Future_Value.

Future_Value is 

Source_value is the productive potential of Sources {land, water, minerals, tools, nature, knowledge, ...}.  This is an Owner_cost

Labor_Value is the productive potential of human effort {work + metawork {automation, permaculture}}.  This is an Owner_cost.



